---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<style>
  .donate {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #1d1d1f;
  }

  /* ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 5.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 55% at 50% 0%,
      rgba(0,113,227,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .donate-eyebrow {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #0071e3;
    background: rgba(0,113,227,0.08);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .donate-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    line-height: 1.06;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 auto 1.1rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .donate-hero p {
    font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.1rem);
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* ── OPEN COLLECTIVE ──────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-oc {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-oc-inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .donate-oc-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; text-align: center; }
    .donate-oc-inner img { margin: 0 auto; }
  }

  .donate-oc-logo {
    height: 165px;
    width: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .donate-oc-text h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .donate-oc-text p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 1.75rem;
  }

  .donate-oc-text .recommended {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #34c759;
    background: rgba(52,199,89,0.1);
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: block;
    width: fit-content;
  }

  /* ── PRIMARY BUTTON ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.6rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #0071e3;
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: background 0.18s, transform 0.18s;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover { background: #0080f5; transform: scale(1.02); }

  /* ── ALTERNATIVES ─────────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-alt {
    background: #ffffff;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .donate-alt-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-alt-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .donate-alt-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }

  .donate-alt-header p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #86868b;
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-note {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .donate-note a { color: #0071e3; text-decoration: none; }
  .donate-note a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .donate-platforms {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) { .donate-platforms { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .donate-platform-card {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    border-radius: 18px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    padding: 1.75rem 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    transition: box-shadow 0.25s, transform 0.25s;
  }

  .donate-platform-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.09);
  }

  .donate-platform-card .plabel {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #86868b;
  }

  .donate-platform-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .btn-patreon {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #F96854;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.18s;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .btn-patreon:hover { background: #f75740; }

  .btn-paypal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 980px;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    background: #0070BA;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.18s;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .btn-paypal:hover { background: #005ea6; }

  /* ── DONORS & GOALS ───────────────────────────────────────── */
  .donate-goals {
    background: #f5f5f7;
    padding: 5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .donate-goals-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .donate-goals-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .donate-goals-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3vw, 2.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #1d1d1f;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .donate-goals-header p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #6e6e73;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  /* Prose body */
  .donate-prose p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
  }

  .donate-prose strong { color: #1d1d1f; font-weight: 600; }

  .donate-prose a { color: #0071e3; text-decoration: none; }
  .donate-prose a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  .donate-prose ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem 1.25rem;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .donate-prose ul li {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    padding-left: 0.25rem;
  }

  /* Funded items */
  .donate-funded {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
    padding: 1.5rem 1.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
  }

  .donate-funded-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.6rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .donate-funded-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .donate-funded-item::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #34c759;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }

  /* Thank you badge */
  .donate-thankyou {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0071e3 0%, #0051a8 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.25rem 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  /* LTS goal items */
  .donate-lts-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    padding: 0.65rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #3a3a3c;
  }

  .donate-lts-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .lts-badge {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 999px;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.55rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .lts-funded   { background: rgba(52,199,89,0.12);  color: #1a7a35; }
  .lts-pending  { background: rgba(255,159,10,0.12); color: #8a5a00; }
  .lts-unfunded { background: rgba(255,59,48,0.10);  color: #9e1c15; }
</style>

<BaseLayout>
<div class="donate">

  <!-- ── HERO ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-hero">
    <span class="donate-eyebrow">
      <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
        <path d="M6 1.5C4 1.5 2 3 2 5c0 3 4 6.5 4 6.5s4-3.5 4-6.5c0-2-2-3.5-4-3.5z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
      </svg>
      Support Ubuntu Budgie
    </span>
    <h1>Help us keep<br/>Budgie flying.</h1>
    <p>Every donation, large or small, helps fund development, infrastructure and the future of Ubuntu Budgie.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ── OPEN COLLECTIVE ───────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-oc">
    <div class="donate-oc-inner">
      <img src="/icons/oc.svg" alt="Open Collective Logo" class="donate-oc-logo" />
      <div class="donate-oc-text">
        <h2>Donate via Open Collective</h2>
        <p>Open Collective is our preferred donation platform. It provides full financial transparency — you can see exactly how every pound is spent, from developer payments to infrastructure costs.</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-primary">
          Donate to our Collective
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2.5 9.5l7-7M9.5 2.5H5M9.5 2.5v4.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── ALTERNATIVES ──────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-alt">
    <div class="donate-alt-inner">
      <div class="donate-alt-header">
        <h2>Other ways to donate</h2>
        <p>Recurring donations and custom one-time donations are both available.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-note">
        Paypal and Patreon are still active, but we encourage supporters to use Open Collective — it has lower commission fees, meaning maximum impact per donation.<br/>
        Special thanks to our fiscal host: <a href="https://opencollective.com/the-social-change-nest" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Social Change Nest</a>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-platforms">

        <div class="donate-platform-card">
          <span class="plabel">Recurring donation</span>
          <h3>Patreon</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#6e6e73;margin:0;line-height:1.55;">Monthly support with exclusive updates for patrons.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn-patreon">
            <svg width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M15.385 1.015c-4.418 0-8 3.582-8 8s3.582 8 8 8 8-3.582 8-8-3.582-8-8-8zM.985 23V1.015h3V23h-3z"/>
            </svg>
            Support on Patreon
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="donate-platform-card">
          <span class="plabel">One-time or monthly</span>
          <h3>PayPal</h3>
          <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#6e6e73;margin:0;line-height:1.55;">Flexible one-time or recurring PayPal donations.</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn-paypal">
            <svg width="14" height="14" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M7.657 21.327h2.613c.484 0 .872-.388.872-.872v-8.13c0-.484-.388-.872-.872-.872H7.657c-.484 0-.872.388-.872.872v8.13c0 .484.388.872.872.872zm14.4-9.002c0-.484-.388-.872-.872-.872h-2.613c-.484 0-.872.388-.872.872v8.13c0 .484.388.872.872.872h2.613c.484 0 .872-.388.872-.872v-8.13zm-7.2 0c0-.484-.388-.872-.872-.872h-2.613c-.484 0-.872.388-.872.872v8.13c0 .484.388.872.872.872h2.613c.484 0 .872-.388.872-.872v-8.13zM0 3.545c0-.484.388-.872.872-.872h2.613c.484 0 .872.388.872.872v16.91c0 .484-.388.872-.872.872H.872c-.484 0-.872-.388-.872-.872V3.545z"/>
            </svg>
            Support on PayPal
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ── DONORS & GOALS ─────────────────────────────────────── -->
  <section class="donate-goals">
    <div class="donate-goals-inner">

      <div class="donate-goals-header">
        <h2>Donors &amp; Goals</h2>
        <p>We support open source and any money raised goes towards open source developers as well as Ubuntu Budgie itself. Full transparency is our goal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="donate-prose">

        <p>Patreon donations are made visible on confirmation at the beginning of the next month. PayPal donations appear as soon as possible after receipt. We invest donations to provide a better product, support our developers, and keep the lights on.</p>

        <div class="donate-thankyou">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.9)"/>
          </svg>
          Thank you — your support means the world to us.
        </div>

        <p>To date, your donations have helped fund:</p>

        <div class="donate-funded">
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Purchase of the budgie-remix.org URL for one year (2016)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Purchase of the ubuntubudgie.org URL for four years (2016–2020)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">budgie-remix.org three year extension (2017–2020)</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Transfer of budgie-remix.org from WordPress to GoDaddy (2017–2020) — fully funded</div>
          <div class="donate-funded-item">Server fees for ubuntubudgie.org 2017 &amp; 2018 — fully funded by our sponsor <strong>DigitalOcean</strong></div>
        </div>

        <p>Server fees for ubuntubudgie.org 2019 — pending sponsorship</p>

        <p><strong>Long-term Goal — LTS Status.</strong> From 18.04, Long-Term Support is an option Ubuntu Budgie would love to provide to all users. To do this we need a financially sound 3-year model for each LTS release.</p>

        <div class="donate-funded">
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-funded">Funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2018–2020 (18.04 LTS)
          </div>
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-funded">Funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2021–2022 (20.04 LTS)
          </div>
          <div class="donate-lts-item">
            <span class="lts-badge lts-unfunded">Not funded</span>
            Expected costs for 2023 (22.04 LTS)
          </div>
        </div>

        <p>Ubuntu Budgie puts you — our community — front and center in everything we do. You can also support Ubuntu Budgie by buying merchandise from our official store on Zazzle: <a href="#">Ubuntu Budgie Store</a></p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</div>
</BaseLayout>